Onion Soup

Ingredients:
    [list]
    [*]Water 1.20 lt
    [*]Meat Broth 0.15lt
    [*]Butter 200g
    [*]Parsley x1
    [*]Onion x2
    [/list]
Steps:
    [olist]
    [*]Slice
        Onion x2
        Garlic x1

    [*]Add to a Cookpot
        Water 1.20lt
        Meat Broth 0.15lt
        Onion Slices x2
        Butter 200g
        Parsley Piece x2

    [*]Boil

    [*]Transfer to Soup Plate
        Mixture 0.20 lt

        [*]Serve Hot